                "latex": "\\begin{array}{|c|c|c|c|c|c|}\n\\hline\np & q & p\\to q & \\lnot q & \\lnot p & \\lnot q\\to\\lnot p \\\\ \\hline\nT & T & T & F & F & T \\\\\nT & F & F & T & F & F \\\\\nF & T & T & F & T & T \\\\\nF & F & T & T & T & T \\\\ \\hline\n\\end{array}"
